{"tid":672563,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖]香港垃圾髮型屋逐個數","createTime":"2018-05-21T06:18:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-21T08:58:24.000Z","uid":132378,"like":10,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"81a3f6ec12a7156b35db7acc64a87ad79565fb61","tid":672563,"uid":132378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T06:18:02.000Z","msg":"屌你老母次次去親剪髮 同個髮型師講話想修剪下啲陰 或者係剪短少少 佢哋就起勢咁剪 剪短到仆街 留陰變all back咁 屌你啦 我留陰就係因為個額頭唔好睇 你而家同我剪撚晒佢 係咪玩鳩我 明明已經同佢講話剪短少少 係少少 唉依家又要俾人笑足一兩個月 係咪做髮型師呢行都係要聾先做得 收兩舊幾水俾個柒頭我 你話八九十蚊就算9數姐<br />\n<br />\n最撚抵死嘅係條友最後會比張卡片我 想我下次再幫襯佢 屌你老母唔好以為自己真係剪得好好先啦 <br />\n下面係其中一間<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/21/141321_aac1f6cadb6788e7a019ffc592468f35.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F21%2F141321_aac1f6cadb6788e7a019ffc592468f35.png&h=b9bef877&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/21/141322_e8fafe68dc71b149fa7edb08819f4eaf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F21%2F141322_e8fafe68dc71b149fa7edb08819f4eaf.png&h=988bb722&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c2d6a7d64cec9e9e246d3b24761d06ae766194b4","tid":672563,"uid":38701,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T06:19:40.000Z","msg":"講到咁仆街你又次次都去？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72bb5f857acce11fee809a3be81e187a7946ea8f","tid":672563,"uid":134418,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T06:19:55.000Z","msg":"影個頭嚟睇吓"},{"pid":"ec9e1e6056e3209c3490ec6fd6c402dd6d997518","tid":672563,"uid":158613,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T06:20:54.000Z","msg":"次次去親剪髮？？<br />\n<br />\n剪得咁差仲要次次去？你係咪傻㗎？"},{"pid":"3e3203696f4896c9d25717461566d840cda8705d","tid":672563,"uid":73422,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T06:22:36.000Z","msg":"剪短少少 可以代表剪得短少少喎<img src=\"/asse